		"description": "<p>This beige liquid smells of old parchment and coffee. When ingested, the drinker&rsquo;s mind latches onto even the most minute details, enabling them to accurately recall information. For the next week, the drinker gains an expertise die to Arcana or History checks made to perform the research downtime activity, and can accurately reproduce or recall details such as names, dates, or other important information in relation to the topic of their research. So long as they are actively engaged in research and under the effects of this draught, they require only 4 hours of sleep to qualify as a long rest.</p>\n<p>Once the effects of this draught wear off, the drinker suffers 2 levels of Strife.</p>",
